item.title: Majk's songs
item.description: Majk (born Kastriot Rexha, 27 November 1990) is a Kosovar rapper, singer and songwriter. Majk first gained fame in 2005 as a member of the then Kosovo rap group TDS, with hit singles such as “Si Manekene” and “Mejrem”.
